MAKEFILES RULES
* Each file (driver and interface.cpp) has a least two rules:
	* make : to compile
	* make clean : to clean ("make clean" of root folder cleans the whole project)
* The driver file (driver.cpp) has two more rules:
	* make run : to run the program
	* make all: to compile the whole project
FILE'S ROLES
* libs/interface.cpp: 
	It contains methods requires that manipulate the database.
	All the methods contained in a namespace called KNNOTH001.
	It contains a struct StudentRecord which represents a student's details.
* driver.cpp:
	Master of the program.
	Contains methods that print the menu, take the user's choice and process it.
